  "keyFeatures": [
    "Embeddable real-time in-app notification Inbox component (React, Next.js, Vue, Angular, Vanilla JS)",
    "Visual no-code workflow builder with multi-step notification sequences",
    "Code-first workflow SDK (Novu Framework) for TypeScript/Node.js",
    "Unified API for email, SMS, push, in-app, and chat channels",
    "Subscriber management with preferences and personalization",
    "Topic-based fan-out for broadcasting to subscriber groups",
    "Digest step to aggregate multiple events into a single notification",
    "Delay/scheduling steps for time-based notification flows",
    "Multi-environment support (development, staging, production)",
    "Provider integrations: SendGrid, Twilio, FCM, Slack, and 50+ others",
    "Outbound webhooks for real-time event streaming",
    "AI Agent Communication Infrastructure (ACI) for conversational agents",
    "Multi-tenancy support for SaaS applications",
    "Activity feed for observability and debugging"
  ],
